# notify-send

![](header.png)

## Installation

```sh
    pip install notify-send
```

## Usage example

```python
    from notify import notification
    notification('body message', title='optinal')
```

## Development setup

```sh
    git clone https://github.com/andreztz/notify-send.git
    cd notify-send
    virtualenv venv
    source venv/bin/activate
    pip install -e .
```

